description: Simmons and Dr. Radcliffe only have hours to save May before she succumbs forever to her mysterious illness
name: Uprising

description: With tension building in the streets of Harlem thanks to ruthless club owner Cottonmouth, Luke finds it increasingly difficult to live a quiet life.
name: Moment of Truth

description: Luke is pulled deeper into the fight for his neighborhood when, as a favor to an old friend, he tries to help a kid who's in trouble with Cottonmouth.
name: Code of the Streets

description: In the aftermath of a chaotic event at a favorite Harlem hangout, Luke heeds the call to action and hits Cottonmouth where he'll feel it most.
name: Who's Gonna Take the Weight?

description: As he rescues a victim of Cottonmouth's vengeance, Luke remembers his earlier life and the conspiracy that led to his superhuman strength.
name: Step in the Arena

description: Cottonmouth strikes back at Luke by taking his vengeance out on the people of Harlem, while detective Knight and Scarfe face an unexpected threat.
name: Just to Get a Rep

description: After Cottonmouth and Scarfe's bloody clash, Luke realizes that saving the community may turn former allies into enemies, and enemies into allies.
name: Suckas Need Bodyguards

description: Mariah's political career comes under fire, and Cottonmouth picks up information that could put Luke on the run.
name: Manifest

description: Mariah's campaigns to turn the city and the police against Luke, and not even Misty or Claire may be able to save him.
name: Blowin' Up the Spot

description: With Luke wounded and on the run, Misty faces a soul-searching interrogation. Mariah's rise to power takes a dark turn.
name: DWYCK

description: Luke gets closer to the truth about Reva and her part in his fate, while Mariah wrestles with morality of her new role. Misty hunts for Luke.
name: Take It Personal

description: In one bold move, a friend from his past puts Luke on the defensive, Misty in dire straits, and Harlem's safety in jeopardy.
name: Now You're Mine

description: Misty digs deeper for the truth as the neighborhood's power players throw the city into confusion.
name: Soliloquy of Chaos

description: With all of Harlem bearing witness, Luke takes on the fight of his life in hopes of emerging as the defender his city needs.
name: You Know My Steez

description: With rumors of a Red Gyarados rampaging in the Lake of Rage, Lance of the Elite Four decides to investigate.
name: The Lake of Rage

deck: Mad Hatter arrives in Gotham to search for his sister.
description: Hypnotist Jervis Tetch/Mad Hatter arrives in Gotham to search for his sister, Alice, and hires Gordon to help find her. Meanwhile, Penguin decides to run for mayor and Bruce's doppelganger begins to channel him, causing some confusion around town.
name: Look Into My Eyes

deck: Barry continues to forget his old life
description: The Reverse-Flash taunts Kid Flash, and warns of repercussions if Barry continues to forget his old life; when disaster strikes, Barry must decide whether to live as Barry Allen or return to his universe as The Flash.
name: Flashpoint

deck: Oliver takes to the streets solo to protect Star City.
description: After Laurel's death and the departures of both Diggle and Thea from Team Arrow, Oliver takes to the streets solo to protect Star City's citizens as the Green Arrow.
name: legacy

description: As Ghost Riders quest for vengeance brings him into an explosive confrontation with S.H.I.E.L.D., Coulson and Mack must rely on an unlikely ally in their time of desperate need; and Daisy reunites with a familiar face to stop the Watchdogs.
name: Let Me Stand Next to Your Fire

description: Proper Japanese Title: (Zamasu to BurakkuFukamaru Futari no Nazo)
name: Zamasu and Black  The Twos Mystery Deepens

description: Proper Japanese Title: (Kaishin Gowasu o MamoreZamasu o Hakaise yo!)
name: Protect Kaishin Gowasu  Destroy Zamasu!

description: Proper Japanese Title: (Futatabi Mirai eAkasareru Gok Burakku no Shtai!!)
name: Back to the Future  Goku Blacks Identity Revealed!!

description: Tyler joins Shelby in auditioning for an open spot on the popular New Zealand band, The N-Zed Boys. Meanwhile, an ally arrives, but not before the Rangers suspect he has an ulterior motive.
name: Silver Secret

description:
When faced with the fast-firing Cavity monster, Riley thinks Chase doesn't take the threat seriously, but soon learns that Chase simply has a different approach.

A monster capable of causing cavities attacks, meanwhile Riley feels as if Chase does not seem to approach the Rangers mission with any real degree of seriousness.
name: The Tooth Hurts

description: In the wake of Team Rockets takeover of the Goldenrod Radio Tower, Detective Lookers investigation leads him to an enigmatic young Trainer.
name: The Legacy

description: The mysterious traveler Eusine explores the legends of Ecruteak Citys Burned Tower and the Pokmon who rose from its ashes.
name: The Reawakening

description: A misunderstanding while baby-sitting Manon leads to a young girl becoming akumatized as the Puppeteer.
name: The Puppeteer

series.name: Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir

deck: Supergirl and superman team up to stop a new threat
description: Supergirl and Clark team up to stop a new threat emerging in Central City; Alex feels left out while Kara's family stays in town; a pod comes crashing down to Earth.
name: The Adventures of Supergirl

description: Penguin gains power as he closes in on the nomination for mayor of Gotham. Meanwhile, Gordon turns Alice in to the GCPD for the bounty. Also, Bruce and Alfred race to find Bruce's doppelganger after learning he's assumed Bruce's identity.
name: New Day Rising

description: Barry discovers that the effects from Flashpoint are greater than he thought. In the meantime, he meets his new co-worker who has an immediate disdain for him.
name: Paradox

deck: Oliver recruits Curtis, Wild Dog and Evelyn Sharp for his team
description: Oliver recruits Curtis, Wild Dog and Evelyn Sharp for his team, but his training methods prove to be too much for some to handle. In flashbacks, Oliver continues his initiation into the Bratva.
name: The Recruits

description: When a new threat emerges, Dr. Nate Heywood seeks out Oliver Queen to help find the scattered Legends; once reunited, they go to 1942, to keep Albert Einstein from being kidnapped before the Nazis destroy New York City with a nuclear bomb.
name: Out of Time

description: When an uninvited guest breaks into their headquarters, Team Magma must race against time to make their ambitions become a reality.
name: The Vision

description: As Robbie Reyes struggles to control The Ghost Rider, S.H.I.E.L.D. infiltrates a high-security prison to unravel the secrets that haunt them all.
name: Lockup

deck: The Enterprise discovers an object that looks like an asteroid, but is in fact a starship unbeknownst to its inhabitants.
description:
The Enterprise is fired upon with missiles originating from what appears to be an asteroid. Upon closer examination it is discovered to be a self-propelled ship heading on a collision course for an inhabited planet.

Meanwhile, Dr. McCoy is diagnosed with an incurable, fatal disease.
name: For the World Is Hollow and I Have Touched the Sky

deck: Supergirl is hurt by a kryptonite-powered villain sent by Cadmus
description: Supergirl is hurt by a kryptonite-powered villain sent by Cadmus to attack National City. Superman blames Hank since the kryptonite was stolen from the DEO. In the meantime, Kara's first day at her new job doesn't go as planned when she meets her new boss.
name: The Last Children of Krypton

deck: Penguin struggles to uphold his promises to the city
description: Crime in Gotham is at an all-time high, as Penguin struggles to uphold his promises to the city. Meanwhile, Butch goes down a dark path with the infamous Red Hood Gang and Bruce begins to investigate Ivy's whereabouts.
name: Anything for You

deck: Wells and Jesse return from Earth-2
description: Just as Wells and Jesse return from Earth-2, Central City is attacked by a new meta with the power to control metal
name: Magenta

My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

deck: Green Arrow is forced to face a powerful new drug
description: The Green Arrow is forced to face a powerful new drug dealer when Wild Dog goes off on his own.
name: A Matter of Trust

description: The Legends discover a time aberration that threatens the Justice Society of America, who are on a mission to intercept and seize a mysterious package in Nazi-occupied Paris.
name: The Justice Society of America

description: Deep under the sea, Team Aquas leader is about to achieve his greatest goal. Can one voice of reason turn the tide of destruction?
name: The Cavern

description: Sandy creates the latest acorn-based food sensation, but her tree pays the price for her greed.
name: Sandy's Nutmare

description: The gang heads to Food Con, but things go awry when they become stranded in the woods.
name: Food Con Castaways

description: SpongeBob puts up a community bulletin board, but anonymous reviews lead to trouble.
name: Bulletin Board

deck: While Tom and his owner are sleeping by the refrigerator, Jerry steals all the food.
name: Little Big Mouse

deck: An elderly museum tour Jerry talks about his part in the Wright brothers' aerial experiments.
name: Kitty Hawked

deck: Tom and Butch are claim jumpers in the 19th Century at a Sutter's Mill, scheming to steal gold from Jerry's claim.
name: 24 Karat Kat

description: The Titans learn about cartoon-style violence in order to get revenge on a snack-stealing squirrel.
name: Squash & Stretch
